SNS Types?

Standard Topic:
  ✅ unlimited throughput
  ✅ at least once delivery
  ⚠️ messages may be out of order
  ⚠️ duplicates possible

FIFO Topic:
  ✅ exactly once delivery
  ✅ strict order guaranteed
  ❌ lower throughput
  ✅ use when order matters
------------------------------------------
SNS Message Filtering?

Without filtering:
  ALL subscribers get ALL messages ❌

With filtering:
  subscribers get ONLY relevant messages ✅

Example:
  SNS Topic receives all orders

  Subscription 1 (Electronics team):
    filter: category = "electronics"
    only gets electronics orders ✅

  Subscription 2 (Clothing team):
    filter: category = "clothing"
    only gets clothing orders ✅
-------------------------------------
 SNS Fan Out Pattern (important!)?

One message → many queues

SNS Topic
    ↓
    ├──→ SQS Queue 1 → Service A processes
    ├──→ SQS Queue 2 → Service B processes
    └──→ SQS Queue 3 → Service C processes

Real example:
  User uploads image
        ↓
  SNS Topic
        ↓
  ├──→ SQS → resize image service
  ├──→ SQS → watermark service
  └──→ SQS → virus scan service

All 3 process same message independently ✅
