SNS vs SQS

SQS                          SNS
────────────────             ────────────────
Queue                        Topic
Pull (consumer pulls)        Push (SNS pushes)
One to One                   One to Many
Stores messages              No storage
Process later                Immediate
Decouple services            Notify many

When to use SQS:
  ✅ background jobs
  ✅ decouple services
  ✅ handle traffic spikes
  ✅ retry failed tasks

When to use SNS:
  ✅ notify multiple systems
  ✅ real time alerts
  ✅ fan out pattern
